#. Max bytes: 194
msgctxt "Offset_0x62194_Len_194"
msgid ""
"The cafe manager will let you feed the cats\n"
"in the store! Wow! You'll even get a gift if\n"
"the cats seem pleased with your offering.\n"
" \n"
"Try out different food to see what gets\n"
"their motors purring!"
msgstr ""
"Il gestore del café ti lascerà nutrire i gatti\n"
"nel locale! Wow! Riceverai anche un dono se\n"
"i gatti gradiranno la tua offerta.\n"
" \n"
"Prova vari cibi per vedere cosa li\n"
"farà fare le fusa!"

